Fix v0.5.0 schema bug: change 'version' to 'specversion' in required fields

The v0.5.0 release has a bug in three schemas where they incorrectly
require 'version' instead of 'specversion' in the context.

This patch fixes:
- pipelinerunfinished.json
- testcaserunfinished.json
- testsuiterunfinished.json

This fix is based on upstream commit ef5bb9c which will be included
in v0.5.1. Once v0.5.1 is released, this patch can be removed.

